casebody.data:
No. 83,

Orig.

Maryland et al. v. Louisiana. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., 445 U. S. 913.]

Motion of the United States for leave to intervene referred to the Special Master. Report of the Special Master received and ordered filed. Exceptions, if any, with supporting briefs to the Report of the Special Master may be filed by the parties within 30 days. Reply briefs, if any, to such exceptions may be filed within 30 days.
